PhotonVision is probably the 2nd easiest, but cheapest way to get April tag detection working. It allows for adding a second camera for just the cost of the second camera.

If you have a LimeLight camera, that’s the easiest, but if you don’t, it’s an expensive investment, and iirc only supports the one camera. Adding a second requires purchasing another LimeLight.
